725319f-a.text:
40th Avenue, west from 21st Street. On the left are the newly-erected Queensbridge Houses, a low-rent governmental project.
P. L. Sperr  September 5, 1940

725120f-a.text:
21st Street, west side, north from and across 40th Avenue. The buildings on the left are on the north side of 40th Avenue and on the right is the paper factory of the Ravenswood Paper Company.
P. L. Sperr  September 5, 1940
